{"tid":381770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠以345億美元續居本港首富 內地首富馬雲排名全球17","createTime":"2017-08-31T08:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T08:25:47.000Z","uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b660aa26f737b4a2578be54e919569bcbd68bca3","tid":381770,"uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:25:47.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠以345億美元續居本港首富 內地首富馬雲排名全球17<br />\n2017/08/31 12:41<br />\n<br />\n福布斯》公布2017年富豪名單，本港富豪排名普遍上升。其中長和(<a href=\"http://00001.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00001.HK&d=%2FNfhDC2D30LZjaqxolDEFQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=28d01904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00001.HK</a>)主席李嘉誠續以345億美元身家居本港富豪榜首，全球排名22位。其次為恆地(<a href=\"http://00012.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00012.HK&d=%2FNfhDC2D30LZjaqxolDEFQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=ec5dad52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00012.HK</a>)主席李兆基，以275億美元身家排名全球30。新地(<a href=\"http://00016.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00016.HK&d=%2FNfhDC2D30LZjaqxolDEFQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=901f5b27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00016.HK</a>)郭氏兄弟則以173億美元排名全球63，於本港富豪中排行第三。<br />\n<br />\n全球首100名富豪中還包括排名81的嘉華(<a href=\"http://00173.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00173.HK&d=%2FNfhDC2D30LZjaqxolDEFQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=59965f2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00173.HK</a>)主席呂志和，排名85的華置(<a href=\"http://00127.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00127.HK&d=%2FNfhDC2D30LZjaqxolDEFQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7b1fde5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00127.HK</a>)劉鑾雄。<br />\n<br />\n內地富豪方面，則以阿里巴巴創辦人馬雲以379億美元居首，全球排名17。騰訊(<a href=\"http://00700.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00700.HK&d=%2FNfhDC2D30LZjaqxolDEFQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=4564b90b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00700.HK</a>)主席兼行政總裁馬化騰以370億美元緊隨其後，全球排名第19。恆大(<a href=\"http://03333.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F03333.HK&d=%2FNfhDC2D30LZjaqxolDEFQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=1cca1e37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">03333.HK</a>)董事長許家印全球排名20，身家347億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬雲唔係有香港身份證咩？點解計佢係大陸人？"}]}